@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.29
    tmp = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.04 + v1 + 0.66)) / (0.38 * 0.88))
    tmp = wp.abs((v2 - wp.cos(v2 + 0.52)))
    tmp = wp.cos((0.65 - (tmp + 0.45 - v2 + 0.31)))
    tmp = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.21 - tmp + 0.02)) / wp.sin((tmp + 0.68 + v1 + 0.09)))
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.49) - 0.32) + 0.34)
    data[tid] = v0
